    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i hear a lot of different things about it. some people say the claims are just part of normal sovereignty disputes and that the west is just stirring up trouble to contain china. why do you frame it as china being \"aggressive\" though? isnt it just a dispute over territory that's been going on for ages?",
